n of a powerful little alien that you may or may not have stolen/liberated from the evil Empire. As the Empire closes in, you'll need to find a way to balance your ship's management with the onslaught of attacks. Do you have what it takes to survive?"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "1324311035174797", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984472_1324311038508130_2610060411856834928_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=C8nvBe9gHVMQ7kNvgHQeAqo&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBAWYoLiHJ68xCaZW0oFjXMEEYz02HdrPU5oOrZnyJ-mg&oe=671782F8"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Portrait.png", "id": "1021944422558335", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031612_1021944425891668_3460677483354056217_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6mG50JPz1joQ7kNvgH9bdvh&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAGkW8vw7yeoU4FNd7YetjWSrsm_L2bz5CrSKPM2AZi9A&oe=671782FE"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Square.png", "id": "998366967853309", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031369_998366971186642_4701792016341896524_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ggJRkNqNbbMQ7kNvgG-LGvR&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDz3hqLdQatM6VxCWAzOWFenjfjsA3JzxeG124y7UcUEg&oe=67179043"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "973425620588096", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86610716_973425627254762_5218087471640407679_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Bgh0eZOlIy8Q7kNvgEPicWb&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDZyzKQsqdwvy3k79TzIAvNWeFJKj2aHwW4zqtNzuPpvg&oe=6717A981"}, {"file_name": "CoverImage_Landscape.png", "id": "822780949101586", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75557065_822780952434919_8573226718553